{"tid":2349671,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"咁Care媒體頒獎禮嘅賽果做咩？","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T02:02:17.000Z","uid":49781,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5693e34880899e21ab2e5eb233e844568b828b24","tid":2349671,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"媒體頒獎禮不嬲俾人話咗係造馬十幾廿年<br />\n<br />\n就算有投票嘅獎都確保唔到係一人一票，又或者未必真係受好多樂迷care（近幾年仲要冇數據公開過）<br />\n<br />\n反正各大收費嘅串流平台都有哂數據邊啲歌先係最Hit最Top<br />\n<br />\n要鬥就鬥Spotify KKBOX Apple Music呢啲<br />\n<br />\n有畀錢聽歌嘅數字先係王道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五台又好四台又好當娛樂Show睇就算<br />\n<br />\n就算要係呢啲頒獎禮講公信力我都只會睇港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080f4751c240a89661ec4c6dc8b37d08ae775605","tid":2349671,"uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"攬實個用dj點播率做標準嘅獎有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0dc90bb0cd466a6c2c334f92d7700fdda60af5","tid":2349671,"uid":49781,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080f4751c240a89661ec4c6dc8b37d08ae775605","tid":2349671,"uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"攬實個用dj點播率做標準嘅獎有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T17:04:31.000Z","msg":"Coolmusic日日mon住個ap次數都可以咁光明正大造馬畀你睇<br />\n<br />\nRemix版再派台嘅又唔知點計<br />\n<br />\nDuet嘅又唔知點計<br />\n<br />\n計數條尺年年都唔同嘅<br />\n<br />\n專業十大又可以左調右調<br />\n<br />\n最誇張都係心之科學贏到未來見個年<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外一提，至尊歌已經變咗關愛座<br />\n<br />\n近十年全部都係老牌歌手，第一嘅永遠唔係我哋心目中嘅第一（我只服重口味、任我行、我們都是這樣長大的）"},{"pid":"972d53817bf865c7a34cf227ce5dcc8aab92d019","tid":2349671,"uid":46018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T17:1